Package squidpony.squidmath

Class FoamyNoise

java.lang.Object
squidpony.squidmath.FoamyNoise
All Implemented Interfaces:
Noise.Noise2D, Noise.Noise3D, Noise.Noise4D, Noise.Noise5D, Noise.Noise6D
@Beta public class FoamyNoise extends Object implements Noise.Noise2D, Noise.Noise3D, Noise.Noise4D, Noise.Noise5D, Noise.Noise6D
A modification of FoamNoise that allows specifying a Noise implementation (or implementations) to use in place of the value noise that FoamNoise uses. A typical use might be to try Classic Perlin Noise or Simplex Noise in place of Value Noise, by passing a ClassicNoise or SeededNoise to the constructor.
